These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, april, august, dominoing
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, tram, van, taxi
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, sunflower, iris, amaryllis
4 different games are played: bridge, domino, billiard, snooker
1. the person driving the tram is the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person playing domino##1
3. the person who growsiris is the person driving the bus##1
4. the person who's birthday is in dominoing is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
5. the person driving the van is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
6. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
7. the person driving the tram is the person playing bridge##1
8. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
9. the person who's birthday is in dominoing is on the left of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Birthday         | december  | dominoing  | april | august |
| Transport           | tram | bus | taxi  | van  |
| Flower   | amaryllis       | iris      | orchid | sunflower      |
| Game           | bridge          | domino     | billiard    | snooker     |

