.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, purple, ivory, blue
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, trike, airplane, snowmobile
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, frog, hamster, lizard
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, may, september, april
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the lizard is the person who's birthday is in july##1
3. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person who likes black##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
5. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
6. the person who likes ivory is the owner of the hamster##1
7. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
8. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who likes black##1
9. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Color      | ivory     | black       | purple | blue        |
| Transport          | snowmobile     | trike       | airplane   | motorbike   |
| Pet   | hamster      | frog       | lizard     | rabbit    |
| Birthday         | september | april | july | may |

