.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, orchid, dahlia, azalea
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, november, july, january
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, baccarat, bongani, prince
House: futuristic, colonial, victorian, modern
 1. the person who growsazalea is the modern house##1
 2. the person who growsdahlia is on the far right##1
 3. the bongani-smoker is on the far right##1
 4. the victorian house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
 5. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
 6. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
 7. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 8. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 9. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the modern house##1
10. the person who growsdahlia is the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Flower      | orchid | bellflower       | azalea        | dahlia        |
| Birthday           | november   | july | february   | january |
| Cigar   | chaman     | baccarat    | prince | bongani        |
| House           | victorian         | futuristic  | modern       | colonial         |

