.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, tea, hot-chocolate, lemonade
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, sports, martial-arts, mystery
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, camping, video-games, cooking
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, october, january, september
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
5. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
7. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
8. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far right##1
9. the person who's birthday is in january is the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Beverage           | tea   | fanta  | lemonade | hot-chocolate |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | mystery       | sports       | action     |
| Hobby   | video-games       | cooking    | camping     | collecting  |
| Birthday           | october     | january | september     | may         |

