.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-5::.
4 different games are played: poker, canasta, snooker, monopoly
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, bike, helicopter, car
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, 7up, milk, almond-milk
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, dannemann, tiparillo, old-henry
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
2. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the person playing poker##1
3. the dannemann-smoker is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
6. the old-henry-smoker is the person drinking milk##1
7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
8. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
9. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Game           | poker  | snooker    | canasta | monopoly |
| Transport   | helicopter      | bike    | bus         | car    |
| Beverage   | 7up   | iced-tea     | milk          | almond-milk      |
| Cigar         | dannemann | vegafina | old-henry      | tiparillo      |

