.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-6::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, apricot, coral, brown
4 different games are played: canasta, domino, go, monopoly
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, photography, writing, dancing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, snowboarding, ice-hockey, tennis
 1. the person who likes coral is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 2. the person who likes white is the person who's hobby is photography##1
 3. the person playing canasta is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person who likes white##1
 5. the person who's hobby is writing is the person playing monopoly##1
 6. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
 7. the person playing go is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 8. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 9. the person playing go is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Color          | white  | brown | coral     | apricot |
| Game           | go  | monopoly      | canasta | domino    |
| Hobby   | photography | writing  | traveling    | dancing  |
| Sport           | ice-hockey   | tennis       | weightlifting       | snowboarding      |

