The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, architect, lawyer, software-developer
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, apricot, purple, orange
4 different games are played: snooker, canasta, mah-jongg, poker
 1. the person who likes white is the architect##1
 2. the person playing poker is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the lawyer##1
 4. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the lawyer##1
 5. the architect is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
 6. the lawyer is on the left of the software-developer##1
 7. the person who likes white is the person playing mah-jongg##1
 8. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left##1
 9. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
10. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Sport    | tennis | swimming     | sailing    | climbing |
| Job       | writer | lawyer    | software-developer | architect |
| Color         | apricot   | purple  | orange        | white    |
| Game   | poker   | canasta | snooker    | mah-jongg |

