4. the british is on the left of the person eating corn##1
5. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
6. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
7. the pakistani is the person eating garlic##1
8. the person eating papaya is the person who's sport is cycling##1
9. the person eating radish is the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |     4      |
| Sport      | soccer      | cycling         | skiing        | climbing      |
| Nationality           | pakistani | british | russian  | mexican  |
| Game   | monopoly    | canasta     | billiard | poker     |
