6. the person who growslily is the aristoff-smoker##1
7. the person who growsmarigold is the electrician##1
8. the person drinking juice is on the far left##1
9. the person drinking almond-milk is the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |     4      |
