.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-10::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, tram, trike, roller
4 different games are played: billiard, canasta, backgammon, whist
There 4 different types of food: tomato, mango, kale, onion
City: new-york, san-francisco, paris, prague
1. the person playing whist is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
2. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the trike is the person playing whist##1
5. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person eating mango##1
6. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
7. the person eating onion is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
8. the person playing canasta is the person driving the roller##1
9. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |      4      |
| Transport      | snowmobile     | roller           | tram    | trike    |
| Game         | backgammon  | canasta | billiard  | whist |
| Food   | kale     | tomato     | mango | onion   |
| City         | prague | new-york     | san-francisco | paris     |

