 6. the person driving the ship is on the far right##1
 7. the person who likes pink is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 8. the person playing poker is the person who likes apricot##1
 9. the person who likes fuchsia is on the far right##1
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4     |
| Transport      | car | roller     | jet-ski          | ship |
| Pet   | guinea-pig   | frog       | bird     | rat   |
| Game   | poker    | scrabble  | whist         | canasta     |
| Color         | apricot | white | pink | fuchsia  |

 